LABEL: CLD BPD

NAME: sc_anemia
LABEL: Have you ever been told by a physician or healthcare provider that you have sickle cell anemia?

NAME: cond_prev_activity
LABEL: Do you have any serious physical or mental condition(s) that limit your ability to perform daily activities?

NAME: hearing
LABEL: Are you deaf or do you have serious difficulty hearing?

NAME: vision
LABEL: Are you blind or do you have serious difficulty seeing, even when wearing glasses?

NAME: memory
LABEL: Because of a physical, mental, or emotional condition, do you have serious difficulty concentrating, remembering, or making decisions? (5 years or older)

NAME: walk_stairs
LABEL: Do you have serious difficulty walking or climbing stairs? (5 years or older)

NAME: dressing_bathing
LABEL: Do you have difficulty dressing or bathing? (5 years or older)

NAME: doctor_shopping
LABEL: Because of a physical, mental, or emotional condition, do you have difficulty doing errands alone such as visiting a doctor's office or shopping? (15 years old or older)

NAME: mental_illness
LABEL: Have you ever been told by a physician, psychologist, or healthcare provider that you have any mental illness (for example depression, anxiety, bipolar, schizophrenia, or other)?

NAME: working
LABEL: We would like to know about what you do-are you working now, looking for work, retired, keeping house, a student, or what?
fmtvals: 1,Working Now|2,Only Temporarily Laid Off, Sick Leave, Or Maternity Leave|3,Looking For Work, Unemployed|4,Retired|5,Disabled, Permanently, Or Temporarily|6,Keeping House|7,Student|99,Other (Specify)

NAME: alcohol
LABEL: How often did you have a drink containing alcohol in the past year?
fmtvals: 0,Never|1,Monthly Or Less|2,Two To Four Times Per Month|3,Two To Three Times Per Week|4,Four Or More Times Per Week

NAME: alcohol_how_many
LABEL: How many drinks containing alcohol did you have on a typical day when you were drinking in the past year?
fmtvals: 1,1 Or 2 Drinks|2,3 Or 4 Drinks|3,5 Or 6 Drinks|4,7 To 9 Drinks|5,10 Or More Drinks

NAME: alcohol_six_or_more
LABEL: How often did you have six or more drinks on one occasion in the past years?

NAME: education
LABEL: What is the highest grade or level of school you have completed or the highest degree you have received?

LABEL: Do you use any tobacco/nicotine products (including cigarettes, cigars, e-cigarettes, etc)?

LABEL: Zipcode-3

NAME: insurance_work
LABEL: Are you covered by insurance through a current or former employer or union (of yours or another family member's)? This would include extension of employer-based insurance after you left a job (ie. coverage under COBRA).

NAME: insurance_direct
LABEL: Are you covered by insurance purchased directly from an insurance company (by you or another family member)? This would include coverage purchased through an exchange or marketplace, such as HealthCare.gov.

NAME: medicare
LABEL: Are you covered by medicare, for people 65 and older, or people with certain disabilities?

NAME: medicaid
LABEL: Are you covered by medicaid, Medical Assistance (MA), the Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP), or any kind of state or government-sponsored assistance plan based on income or a disability? Sometimes different states have specific names for their med

NAME: tricare
LABEL: Are you covered by TRICARE, Veterans Affairs (VA) healthcare or other military healthcare or health insurance?

NAME: indian_health
LABEL: Are you covered by Indian Health Service?

NAME: insurance_not_covered
LABEL: Does this mean you currently have no health insurance or health coverage plan? In answering this question, please exclude plans that pay for only one type of service (such as, nursing home care, accidents, family planning, or dental care) and plans that on
fmtvals: 0,I Do Not Have Health Insurance|1,I Have Some Kind Of Health Insurance
